value.string: Aston implemented a unit remodel for kitchen and bathrooms in order to maintain their AAA 3-diamond rating. Owner followed the remodel guidelines and remains in the Aston Rental Program. Kaanapali Shores boasts direct beach front location with western exposure offering year round sunset views. Enjoy the lush tropical landscaping and 2 fresh water swimming pools with hydro spa. Amenities include full health club, beach front restaurant and resort retail shops. Maintenance fees include All utilities. E.G. electric, (central A/C), water, sewer, trash, wi-fi access, cable TV, local phone service, storm, flood and general liability insurance. The maintenance fees also include a monthly contribution to the Capital Reserve Fund for major components to the building E.G. roofs, painting, pools, spas and other amenities. All this is paid for with 1 check per month.

The interior living space at 806 square feet is HUGE for a one bedroom condo in Maui. The condo is luxuriously appointed having been recently renovated to the highest level. Kaanapali Shores is a destination condominium resort on the north end of Kaanapali Beach one of the most romantic walking beaches in the world. It has 2 swimming pools, hot tubs, an oceanfront restaurant, a fitness center, salon, ocean side massage, tennis courts, shops, barbeques and FREE internet for owners and guests. The condo is in the Aston rental program with super high occupancy. So check with your agent for details and a showing.

Enjoy Inspiring Views of the Ocean, Breaking Waves & the Island of Molokai from this completely renovated 964 s.f, fee simple, two bedroom, two bath unit overlooking the center courtyard & lush tropical gardens. Close to Maui's finest golf courses, fine dining, hiking, & water sports!
